<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1561566-in-looking-at-the-reviews-it-seems-the">In looking at the reviews, it seems the guys liked it and the women not as much. Is this mostly a story about an older man reliving his sexual exploits of his younger days?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1561566'><a id="like_count_community_question_1561566" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1561566?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F294081.The_Mambo_Kings_Play_Songs_of_Love">like</a></span>

